<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
       font-family: Segoe UI; 
      }
      .container {
        padding: 30px;
        height: fit-content;
        border-radius: 5px 5px 0px 0px;
      }
      .container-success {
        background: #B7F5D280;
        border-top: 5px solid #4BCA81;
      }
      .container-warning {
        background: #fcf3e0;
        border-top: 5px solid #d79301;
      }
      .container-reminder {
        background: #B7DFF5;
        border-top: 5px solid #1178B1;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px;
        background: white;
      }
      .details-box {
        border: 1px solid #C9C9C9;
      }
      .padding-left-right-small {
        padding: 0px 20px;
      }
      .horizontal-bar {
        height: 1px;
        background: #C9C9C9;
      }
      .table-container td{
        padding: 10px;
        font-size: 12px;
      }
      .scheduled-time-cell {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .margin-right-xx_small {
        margin-right: 5px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
            <div class="container container-reminder">
                <div class="content">
                    <p>
                        שלום, [[RECIPIENT_NAME]],
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        כדי להשלים את תהליך הקביעה של פעילות השירות ולהבטיח את המועד שלך, עליך לשלם עבור הפגישה.
                    </p>
                <div class="details-box">
                    <p class="padding-left-right-small">
                        פרטי הפגישה
                    </p>
                    <div class="horizontal-bar"></div>
                    <div class="table-container">
                        <table>
                            <tr>
                                <td>
                                    נקבעה ל:
                                </td>
                                <td class="scheduled-time-cell">
                                    <img src="https://test.salesforce.com/img/icon/t4v35/utility/event_60.png" height="15" class="margin-right-xx_small">
                                    <b>{!DATETIMEVALUE(ServiceAppointment.SchedStartTime)} - {!DATETIMEVALUE(ServiceAppointment.SchedEndTime)} {!User.TimeZoneSidKey}</b>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>
                                    נושא הפגישה:
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <b>{!ServiceAppointment.WorkType}</b>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>
                                    פגישה עם:
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <b>{!ServiceResource.Name}</b>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>
                                    סוג ביקור:
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <b>{!ServiceAppointment.AppointmentType}</b>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p>
                    <a target="_blank" href="{!PaymentLink.PaymentUrl}">עליך להשלים את התשלום</a> בסך <b>[[CURRENCY]] [[AMOUNT]]</b>.
                </p>
                    <p>
                        תודה!
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
          </body>
</html>